<p><strong>Best time to go:</strong> Mid-May to October. With warmer temperatures in July and August - you can cool off with high altitude walks.</p>
<p><strong>Best for:</strong> Challenging walks, families, nature, activities, food &amp; drink</p>
<p><strong>Arrive into:</strong> Geneva Airport or Self-Drive</p>
<p><strong>Travel from: </strong>Gatwick, Heathrow, Manchester, Luton, Bristol, Birmingham and Edinburgh Airports or Self-Drive</p>
