<p><strong>Resort card:</strong> Chamonix Guest card, free at all hotels</p>
<p><strong>24/7 Support and advice:</strong> In person or over the phone from our local resort team based in Chamonix</p>
<p><strong>Inghams Guided Walks included</strong></p>]]></insidersGuide>
